梅尔·吉布森感谢小罗伯特·唐尼在反犹太主义丑闻后的支持https://www.nme.com/news/film/mel-gibson-thanks-robert-downey-jr-for-support-following-anti-semitism-scandal-3615414?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=mel-gibson-感谢小罗伯特·唐尼对以下反犹太主义丑闻的支持Elizabeth AubreyTue, 09 Apr 2024 13:49:17 +0000 Film NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3615414 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Robert-Downey-Jr-and-Mel-Gibson.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="小罗伯特·唐尼和梅尔·吉布森" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Robert-Downey-Jr-and-Mel-Gibson.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Robert-Downey-Jr-and-Mel-Gibson-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Robert-Downey-Jr-and-Mel-Gibson-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Robert-Downey-Jr-and-Mel-Gibson-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Robert-Downey-Jr-and-Mel-Gibson-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Robert-Downey-Jr-and-Mel-Gibson-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “他站起来为我说话。这是一个大胆、慷慨和友善的举动”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/mel-gibson-thanks-robert-downey-jr-for-support-following-anti-semitism-scandal-3615414">梅尔·吉布森感谢小罗伯特·唐尼在反犹太主义丑闻后的支持的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Robert-Downey-Jr-and-Mel-Gibson.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="小罗伯特·唐尼和梅尔·吉布森" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Robert-Downey-Jr-and-Mel-Gibson.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Robert-Downey-Jr-and-Mel-Gibson-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Robert-Downey-Jr-and-Mel-Gibson-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Robert-Downey-Jr-and-Mel-Gibson-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Robert-Downey-Jr-and-Mel-Gibson-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Robert-Downey-Jr-and-Mel-Gibson-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mel-gibson">梅尔·吉布森</a>感谢<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/rober-downey-jr">小罗伯特·唐尼</a>在过去因反犹太主义被捕的丑闻后给予的支持。</p><p>在<a href="https://www.esquire.com/entertainment/a60314472/robert-downey-jr-interview-2024/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i>《时尚</i></a>先生》刊登的与小唐尼的新封面故事中，吉布森形容唐尼“大胆、慷慨、善良”，因为他在 2006 年发表反犹太言论后敦促好莱坞原谅他。</p><p> “有一次，我陷入了一个有点棘手的境地，几乎结束了我的职业生涯，”吉布森告诉<em>《时尚先生》</em> 。 “我在警车后座喝醉了，说了一些蠢话，然后突然间：被列入黑名单。我是取消的海报男孩。</p><p> “几年后，[罗伯特]邀请我获得他获得的某种奖项——我们总是有这种跷跷板的事情，如果他在马车上，我就会掉下来，如果我在马车上，他要掉下来了。”</p><p>他继续说道：“所以当时我在好莱坞几乎不存在，他站起来为我说话。这是一个大胆、慷慨和善意的举动。我因此而爱他。” </p><figure id="attachment_3615418" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3615418" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3615418" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Robert-Downey-Jr-and-Mel-Gibson-Photo-by-Eric-Charbonneau_WireImage.jpg" alt="小罗伯特·唐尼和梅尔·吉布森" width="2000" height="1269" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Robert-Downey-Jr-and-Mel-Gibson-Photo-by-Eric-Charbonneau_WireImage.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Robert-Downey-Jr-and-Mel-Gibson-Photo-by-Eric-Charbonneau_WireImage-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Robert-Downey-Jr-and-Mel-Gibson-Photo-by-Eric-Charbonneau_WireImage-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Robert-Downey-Jr-and-Mel-Gibson-Photo-by-Eric-Charbonneau_WireImage-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Robert-Downey-Jr-and-Mel-Gibson-Photo-by-Eric-Charbonneau_WireImage-1392x883.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Robert-Downey-Jr-and-Mel-Gibson-Photo-by-Eric-Charbonneau_WireImage-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3615418" class="wp-caption-text">小罗伯特·唐尼和梅尔·吉布森 – 图片来源：Eric Charbonneau/WireImage/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>吉布森指的是 2011 年美国电影资料馆颁奖典礼，年度奖项获得者小唐尼在演讲中谈到了吉布森的遭遇。</p><p>他请求好莱坞与他一起“原谅我的朋友的过错，为[吉布森]提供你给我的同样干净的石板，并允许他继续为我们的集体艺术做出伟大而持续的贡献，而不感到羞耻”，指的是他的法律麻烦90年代，这导致他入狱。</p><p>在其他消息中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/robert-downey-jr-would-happily-play-iron-man-again-3614939">小唐尼最近透露，如果有机会，他将重返漫威电影宇宙</a>。</p><p>他因出演 10 部钢铁侠电影而获得全球认可，其中包括 2019 年的<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/avengers-endgame"><em>《复仇者联盟：终局之战》</em></a> 。</p><p>早在三月，小唐尼就凭借在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/christopher-nolan">克里斯托弗·诺兰</a>广受好评的传记片《<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/oppenheimer-review-christopher-nolan-3470392"><em>奥本海默</em></a>》中扮演刘易斯·施特劳斯一角<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/oscars-2024-winners-full-list-3599250">，赢得了他的第一个奥斯卡最佳男配角奖</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/mel-gibson-thanks-robert-downey-jr-for-support-following-anti-semitism-scandal-3615414">梅尔·吉布森感谢小罗伯特·唐尼在反犹太主义丑闻后的支持的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
